## Step 6: Generate Execution Log

Create `execution-log.md`:

```markdown
# Execution Log

| Segment | Est. Complexity | Risk | Cycles Used | Status | Notes |
|---------|----------------|------|-------------|--------|-------|
| 1: <title> | Medium | 4/10 | -- | pending | -- |
| 2: <title> | Low | 2/10 | -- | pending | -- |

**Deep-verify result:** --
**Follow-up plans:** --
```

